## Installation

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone <repository-url>
cd {{package_name}}

# Make the script executable
chmod +x src/main.sh

# Optional: Add to your PATH
ln -s "$(pwd)/src/main.sh" /usr/local/bin/{{package_name}}
```

## Usage

```bash
# Run the script
./src/main.sh

# Show help
./src/main.sh --help

# Show version
./src/main.sh --version
```

